<p>CHAPTER 27 - DETERMINING RATES OF PAYMENT - Immediate Annuities. See guideline 27.13637.</p>
<p>Rollover of annuity - upper limit amount, 1995/96 figure as advised by the Australian Taxation Office.</p>
