<h2>Update 436G # Date 10 August 1995</h2>
<p>CHAPTER 27 - DETERMINING RATES OF PAYMENT - Asset valuation of commercial bills. See guidelines 27.15430 to 27.15435.</p>
<p>The face value of commercial bills is the value to be maintained under the assets test.</p>
