<h2 id="13july1995">Update 417G # Date 13 July 1995</h2>
<p>CHAPTER 41 - PARENTING ALLOWANCE - New chapter. see guidelines 41.000 to 41.14100.</p>
<p>Parenting Allowance (PgA) is a new payment (available from 1 July 1995) that was announced in the White Paper on Employment and Growth in May 1994. PgA replaces Home Child Care Allowance (HCCA), and although the PgA chapter will replace the HCCA chapter, the HCCA chapter will remain available until at least the end of September 1995 to allow processing of outstanding claims.</p>
